Deployment of Django - find out:
-------------
How to :
* Have a seperate setting for development and deployment databases in settings.py
* Have not to restart apache everytime cdoe changes 
 -- use WSGIDaemonProcess
* Have print statements work without causing exception of sys.stdout with mod_wsgi
 http://code.google.com/p/modwsgi/wiki/ConfigurationDirectives#WSGIRestrictStdout
* A way to control the session... different at different computers for diffeent users.. 


